              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-700">When pipes burst at midnight, you show up first. We run around-the-clock campaigns targeting emergency plumbing searches so you capture every urgent call in your area.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
            <div class="h-1 bg-rebel-green"></div>
            <div class="p-8">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-10 text-rebel-green flex-shrink-0">
