                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12 2.25c-5.385 0-9.75 4.365-9.75 9.75s4.365 9.75 9.75 9.75 9.75-4.365 9.75-9.75S17.385 2.25 12 2.25ZM12.75 6a.75.75 0 0 0-1.5 0v.816a3.836 3.836 0 0 0-1.72.756c-.712.566-1.112 1.35-1.112 2.178 0 .829.4 1.612 1.113 2.178.502.4 1.102.647 1.719.756v2.978a2.536 2.536 0 0 1-.921-.421l-.879-.66a.75.75 0 0 0-.9 1.2l.879.66c.533.4 1.169.645 1.821.75V18a.75.75 0 0 0 1.5 0v-.81a4.124 4.124 0 0 0 1.821-.749c.745-.559 1.179-1.344 1.179-2.191 0-.847-.434-1.632-1.179-2.191a4.122 4.122 0 0 0-1.821-.75V8.354c.29.082.559.213.786.393l.415.33a.75.75 0 0 0 .933-1.175l-.415-.33a3.836 3.836 0 0 0-1.719-.755V6Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">High-Ticket Job Targeting</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Drain cleaning pays the bills, but repiping and water heater replacements build your business. We create campaigns that attract the high-value jobs that actually grow your revenue.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
            <div class="h-1 bg-rebel-green"></div>
            <div class="p-8">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-10 text-rebel-green flex-shrink-0">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="m11.54 22.351.07.04.028.016a.76.76 0 0 0 .723 0l.028-.015.071-.041a16.975 16.975 0 0 0 1.144-.742 19.58 19.58 0 0 0 2.683-2.282c1.944-1.99 3.963-4.98 3.963-8.827a8.25 8.25 0 0 0-16.5 0c0 3.846 2.02 6.837 3.963 8.827a19.58 19.58 0 0 0 2.682 2.282 16.975 16.975 0 0 0 1.145.742ZM12 13.5a3 3 0 1 0 0-6 3 3 0 0 0 0 6Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Service Area Domination</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-700">SEO and Google Business Profile optimization get you ranking across your entire service area. When homeowners search "plumber near me," you show up—in every city you serve.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
            <div class="h-1 bg-rebel-green"></div>
            <div class="p-8">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-10 text-rebel-green flex-shrink-0">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.603 3.799A4.49 4.49 0 0 1 12 2.25c1.357 0 2.573.6 3.397 1.549a4.49 4.49 0 0 1 3.498 1.307 4.491 4.491 0 0 1 1.307 3.497A4.49 4.49 0 0 1 21.75 12a4.49 4.49 0 0 1-1.549 3.397 4.491 4.491 0 0 1-1.307 3.497 4.491 4.491 0 0 1-3.497 1.307A4.49 4.49 0 0 1 12 21.75a4.49 4.49 0 0 1-3.397-1.549 4.49 4.49 0 0 1-3.498-1.306 4.491 4.491 0 0 1-1.307-3.498A4.49 4.49 0 0 1 2.25 12c0-1.357.6-2.573 1.549-3.397a4.49 4.49 0 0 1 1.307-3.497 4.49 4.49 0 0 1 3.497-1.307Zm7.007 6.387a.75.75 0 1 0-1.22-.872l-3.236 4.53L9.53 12.22a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06l2.25 2.25a.75.75 0 0 0 1.14-.094l3.75-5.25Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Trust & Reputation Building</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Homeowners don't let just anyone into their home. We build your online reputation with reviews, professional branding, and authority positioning that makes you the obvious choice.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services for Plumbers Section -->
    <section class="py-16 md:py-24 section-checkers">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">
            Marketing Services for <span class="text-rebel-green">Plumbing Contractors</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            Everything you need to capture emergency calls, win high-ticket jobs, and build authority in your market.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Website + Landing Pages -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center mb-20">
          <div>
            <img
              src="https://RebelApeCDN.b-cdn.net/website-landers.webp"
              alt="Plumbing Website Design"
              class="w-full rounded-lg"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="inline-block bg-rebel-green text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-4">Website Design</div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
              Plumbing Websites That <span class="text-rebel-green">Convert</span>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
              Your website needs to do one thing: get the phone to ring. We build fast, professional plumbing websites that establish trust and turn visitors into calls—especially during emergencies.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-4 mb-6">
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <GreenCheck />
                <span class="text-gray-700">Click-to-call buttons prominently displayed</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <GreenCheck />
                <span class="text-gray-700">Service pages for every plumbing service you offer</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <GreenCheck />
                <span class="text-gray-700">Location pages for every city in your service area</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <GreenCheck />
                <span class="text-gray-700">Mobile-optimized for homeowners searching on phones</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <Button text="Learn More About Websites" icon="learn" href="/services/website-design/" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- PPC -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center mb-20">
          <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
            <div class="inline-block bg-rebel-green text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-4">PPC Advertising</div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
              Google Ads That <span class="text-rebel-green">Capture Emergency Calls</span>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
              When someone searches "emergency plumber near me" at 2 AM, you need to be there. We manage Google Ads and Local Service Ads to capture every urgent call and high-value lead in your area.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-4 mb-6">
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <GreenCheck />
                <span class="text-gray-700">24/7 emergency plumbing campaigns</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <GreenCheck />
                <span class="text-gray-700">High-ticket service targeting (repiping, water heaters)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <GreenCheck />
                <span class="text-gray-700">Local Service Ads with Google Guaranteed badge</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <GreenCheck />
                <span class="text-gray-700">Call tracking so you know exactly what's working</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <Button text="Learn More About PPC" icon="learn" href="/services/ppc/" />
          </div>
          <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
            <img
              src="https://rebelapecdn.b-cdn.net/ppc-google-ads.webp"
              alt="Plumbing Google Ads"
              class="w-full rounded-lg"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SEO -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center mb-20">
          <div>
            <img
              src="https://RebelApeCDN.b-cdn.net/featured-outrank-competitors-in-google.webp"
              alt="Plumbing SEO"
              class="w-full rounded-lg"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="inline-block bg-rebel-green text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-4">SEO Services</div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
              Rank #1 for <span class="text-rebel-green">"Plumber Near Me"</span>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
              Long-term authority building through local SEO. We optimize your website and Google Business Profile so you show up first when homeowners search for plumbing services—organically, without paying per click.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-4 mb-6">
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <GreenCheck />
                <span class="text-gray-700">Google Business Profile optimization</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <GreenCheck />
                <span class="text-gray-700">Local keyword targeting for your service areas</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
